{"tid":1181362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［月經］一人一個尷尬到想搵窿捐嘅經歷","createTime":"2019-06-01T14:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T14:59:04.000Z","uid":237123,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b974c42cbcd3d759db6ec22475487d18f1eb6019","tid":1181362,"uid":237123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同親戚食飯臨走前一齊順便去個廁所<br />\n一如既往咁擺好個井字陣就放返個電話入褲袋然後放心哂坐落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知屙完一起身個下聽到 &ldquo;懂&rdquo;一聲就知賴嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我！跌！左！部！電！話！落！屎！坑！</span></span><br />\n原本係出面排住隊吹水嘅親戚們即刻靜左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然不幸中之大幸我個部係plus得個角落左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係當事我個心太亂，第一反應係9秒9拎返部機上嚟<br />\n然後，有一串水花衝出嚟，完美帶到去隔離格嘅地面<br />\n之後我唔敢面對，一直自閉到啲親戚走哂我先出廁所<br />\n啲親戚非常貼心地冇開口問我點解去咁耐，而我就默默咁冇再開過口講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸:個廁所得2格<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634ad903fd52ea266bec3a579c4fbb763f11f5a5","tid":1181362,"uid":203797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"去旅行買野<br />\n同啲fd分開行 佢攞住個購物籃<br />\n我揀完野之後去搵佢<br />\n一野擺左自己啲野入個籃度<br />\n仲大大聲：喂搵左你好耐！我要買呢啲呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一睇<br />\n原來認錯左人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我仲擺曬啲野落佢個籃度<br />\n我望到佢O曬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當下好心急 唔記得自己唔喺香港<br />\n用左廣東話同人講對唔住認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再九秒九撈走自己啲野<br />\n<br />\n我轉身嗰下 聽到佢同我講：唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來對方都係香港人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽呀認錯人真係好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6e162b561f162f10d0f37063339003ab182b80","tid":1181362,"uid":237123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"634ad903fd52ea266bec3a579c4fbb763f11f5a5","tid":1181362,"uid":203797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"去旅行買野<br />\n同啲fd分開行 佢攞住個購物籃<br />\n我揀完野之後去搵佢<br />\n一野擺左自己啲野入個籃度<br />\n仲大大聲：喂搵左你好耐！我要買呢啲呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一睇<br />\n原來認錯左人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我仲擺曬啲野落佢個籃度<br />\n我望到佢O曬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當下好心急 唔記得自己唔喺香港<br />\n用左廣東話同人講對唔住認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再九秒九撈走自己啲野<br />\n<br />\n我轉身嗰下 聽到佢同我講：唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來對方都係香港人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽呀認錯人真係好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最慘係對方聽得明你講乜"},{"pid":"27cf1e4d295603522c3b66d8f2a95e59e49e9d50","tid":1181362,"uid":160348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"托人幫手做啲嘢<br />\nEmail 左佢thank you <br />\n佢答返don't mention it <br />\n我順理成張話，yes I won't tell anyone about this <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211dd7a664504e56b